display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex> acts on a space <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex> acts on <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[G^{\Delta _n}\times  X]]></fr:tex> by
    <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[       g\cdot (g_0,\ldots ,g_n,x)       = (g_0g^{-1},\ldots ,g_ng^{-1},gx).     ]]></fr:tex>
    We denote by <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[[X/G]_\bullet ]]></fr:tex> the simplicial space

    <fr:tree
toc="true"
numbered="false"
show-heading="true"
show-metadata="false"
expanded="true"
root="false"
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"><fr:frontmatter><fr:anchor>2259</fr:anchor><fr:addr
