display="block"><![CDATA[           \operatorname {H}^\bullet (X,G;F)           = \operatorname {H}^\bullet (X/G,F^{-1})         \tag{6.1.2.4}         ]]></fr:tex></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>

      (for a principal homogeneous space).
      This generalises <fr:ref
addr="hodge-theory-iii-6.1.2.2"
href="hodge-theory-iii-6.1.2.2.xml"
taxon="Equation"
number="6.1.2.2" /> (which is the case <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F=\underline {\mathbb {Z}}]]></fr:tex>).
    </html:li>

  </html:ol>
